<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>NorthCraft | New Lead</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    margin:0;
    padding:40px 15px;
    background:#f6f3ed;
    font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
    color:#243128;
}

table{
    border-collapse:collapse;
}

.email-container{
    width:700px;
    max-width:700px;
    background:#ffffff;
    border:1px solid #d8c28b;
    border-radius:18px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

/* ========================================================= */

.hero{

    background:#0d342d;

    padding:60px 55px;

    text-align:center;

    border-bottom:6px solid #c8a75d;
}

.brand-tag{

    display:inline-block;

    padding:8px 18px;

    border:1px solid rgba(255,215,140,.35);

    color:#edd7a1;

    font-size:11px;

    letter-spacing:3px;

    text-transform:uppercase;

    border-radius:30px;

    margin-bottom:35px;

}

.monogram{

    width:95px;

    height:95px;

    line-height:95px;

    margin:0 auto 18px;

    border:2px solid #c8a75d;

    border-radius:50%;

    font-size:42px;

    color:#f1d894;

    font-weight:bold;

}

.hero h1{

    font-size:44px;

    color:#edd7a1;

    letter-spacing:4px;

    margin-bottom:12px;

    font-weight:normal;

}

.tagline{

    color:#f5ebd2;

    font-size:14px;

    letter-spacing:2px;

    text-transform:uppercase;

}

.gold-divider{

    width:90px;

    height:2px;

    background:#c8a75d;

    margin:28px auto;

}

.hero h2{

    color:#ffffff;

    font-size:30px;

    margin-bottom:18px;

    font-weight:normal;

}

.hero-text{

    color:#ece4cf;

    line-height:30px;

    font-size:16px;

}

/* ========================================================= */

.section{

    padding:45px 45px 20px;

}

.section h3{

    font-size:22px;

    color:#0d342d;

    margin-bottom:25px;

    border-left:5px solid #c8a75d;

    padding-left:15px;

}

/* ========================================================= */

.info-card{

    background:#faf8f3;

    border:1px solid #d8c28b;

    border-radius:14px;

    padding:22px;

}

.label{

    color:#9f7b2b;

    font-size:11px;

    text-transform:uppercase;

    letter-spacing:2px;

    margin-bottom:10px;

    font-weight:bold;

}

.value{

    font-size:19px;

    color:#243128;

    line-height:28px;

    word-break:break-word;

}

/* ========================================================= */

.message-card{

    background:#faf8f3;

    border:1px solid #d8c28b;

    border-left:6px solid #c8a75d;

    border-radius:16px;

    padding:35px;

}

.quote-mark{

    font-size:52px;

    color:#d0b16b;

    line-height:30px;

    margin-bottom:12px;

}

.message-card p{

    font-size:17px;

    color:#37463d;

    line-height:34px;

    white-space:pre-wrap;

}

/* ========================================================= */

.reminder{

    padding:45px;

    background:#133f35;

    color:#ffffff;

}

.reminder h3{

    color:#f1d894;

    margin-bottom:16px;

    font-size:24px;

    font-weight:normal;

}

.reminder p{

    line-height:30px;

    color:#ece4cf;

    font-size:16px;

}

/* ========================================================= */

.footer{

    background:#0d342d;

    text-align:center;

    padding:55px 40px;

}

.footer-logo{

    width:70px;

    height:70px;

    line-height:70px;

    margin:0 auto 18px;

    border-radius:50%;

    border:2px solid #c8a75d;

    color:#f1d894;

    font-size:30px;

    font-weight:bold;

}

.footer h2{

    color:#edd7a1;

    letter-spacing:4px;

    font-size:34px;

    margin-bottom:15px;

    font-weight:normal;

}

.footer p{

    color:#ece4cf;

    line-height:28px;

    font-size:15px;

}

.footer-divider{

    width:110px;

    height:2px;

    background:#c8a75d;

    margin:28px auto;

}

.footer-tagline{

    letter-spacing:2px;

    text-transform:uppercase;

    color:#edd7a1;

}

.footer-badge{

    display:inline-block;

    margin-top:25px;

    background:#c8a75d;

    color:#143229;

    padding:12px 24px;

    border-radius:30px;

    font-size:13px;

    font-weight:bold;

    letter-spacing:1px;

}

/* ========================================================= */

@media only screen and (max-width:700px){

.email-container{

    width:100% !important;

}

.hero{

    padding:40px 25px;

}

.hero h1{

    font-size:34px;

}

.hero h2{

    font-size:24px;

}

.section{

    padding:30px 22px 15px;

}

.reminder{

    padding:30px 22px;

}

.footer{

    padding:40px 25px;

}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<tr>

<td align="center">

<table class="email-container" role="presentation" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- HERO -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="hero">

<div class="brand-tag">

NEW LEAD NOTIFICATION

</div>

<div class="monogram">

NC

</div>

<h1>

NORTHCRAFT

</h1>

<p class="tagline">

Curated • Thoughtful • Memorable

</p>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<h2>

🎁 A New Premium Enquiry Has Arrived

</h2>

<p class="hero-text">

A potential customer has shown interest in NorthCraft's premium gifting experience.

Review the details below and connect with the customer at the earliest opportunity.

</p>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- CUSTOMER DETAILS -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="section">

<h3>

Customer Information

</h3>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

FULL NAME

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= name %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td height="18"></td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

EMAIL ADDRESS

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= email %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td height="18"></td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

PHONE NUMBER

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= phone %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- MESSAGE -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="section">

<h3>

Customer Requirements

</h3>

<div class="message-card">

<div class="quote-mark">

"

</div>

<p>

<%= message %>

</p>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- REMINDER -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="reminder">

<h3>

✨ Recommended Action

</h3>

<p>

Respond within the next <strong>30–60 minutes</strong>.

Fast responses significantly increase the chances of converting this enquiry into a successful corporate gifting opportunity.

</p>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- FOOTER -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="footer">

<div class="footer-logo">

NC

</div>

<h2>

NORTHCRAFT

</h2>

<p>

Premium Corporate Gifting

</p>

<p>

Luxury Hampers • Festive Collections • Employee Welcome Kits

</p>

<div class="footer-divider"></div>

<p class="footer-tagline">

Curated • Thoughtful • Memorable

</p>

<div class="footer-badge">

Premium Lead Notification

</div>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</body>

</html>
